Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但去那裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:29.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找出CIA和「{\1c&H0000FF}蛇{\r}」勾結的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.97,0:02:32.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告發相關者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:35.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但會這麼順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「{\1c&H000000\3c&HFFFFFF\bord2}花園計劃{\r}」若被公諸於世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:42.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府也沒法無視被害者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必也能弄到藥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:47.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:48.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芸芸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:49.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是生命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:50.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:52.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:58.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:01.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:02.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有留言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:07.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「你真正的名字是{\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}絕望{\r}」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:09.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord2}絕望{\r}？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:12.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南完全沒有絕望的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:14.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飯吃的不少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:17.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屬於豐滿健康的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:18.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一點也不高興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:19.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:21.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部再豐滿點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:22.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:23.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波霸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你沒資格說我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點緊張感都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:29.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:32.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我感覺就這樣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:36.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了防止被外人覺察
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然挖通遺跡內部修建設施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好誇張的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:04:00.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望入侵路線和我在時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:07.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好一件武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:09.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:14.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防身用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:18.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:22.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:26.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我等成老太婆怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:31.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在接受姐姐大人的疼愛之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:32.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.24,0:04:35.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你做防老化處理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:39.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你一生不會變老
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來還在使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:54.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方是故意門戶大開的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要破壞一切
