Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感覺到她的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顏色？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.84,0:05:18.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的感覺恢復了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
