Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.07,0:05:33.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都看不到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:48.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:52.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣 已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:06:00.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在上海協助逃亡的「花苞」還有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:05.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.17,0:06:14.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:19.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只留下我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:20.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:21.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我挑這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定也能做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:27.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:29.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看像什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪獸的恆齒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋸齒怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,業火熊熊的地獄之門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:40.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的都是些可怕的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:42.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裡真的很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芸芸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:47.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說能做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:50.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:55.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試試看才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:05.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看迦南吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:07.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看迦南？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看到迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣就湧出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一看到那傢伙就想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:16.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:17.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:18.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到某個男人時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有相同的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:25.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要說這種感受叫什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:30.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是來阻止梁琪大人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要看時機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:59.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直後悔把你交給那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道這裡是為何而生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:06.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是為了那個小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:11.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創造出第二個迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:19.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,UA病毒將那個小姑娘的聯覺昇華到了新境界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:24.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們被迫走上了迦南的老路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:25.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去了為人的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淪為醜陋而扭曲的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多麼可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:38.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若不是迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所愛的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所愛的村莊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:44.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所愛的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便出手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:53.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們是無辜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:53.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:56.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正義必勝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:09.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:12.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:18.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想贖罪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:19.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:20.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.47,0:09:26.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有悲劇和淚水的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:29.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:31.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒那個怪物的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:33.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:36.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我並肩作戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:41.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為消失的村民們獻上憑弔的鮮花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:46.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓迦南的鮮血之花在「{\1c&H00FF00}花園{\r}」盛開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南可能確實是開端
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:59.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害我們落得這個下場的是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:00.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南為了保護重要之人而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她和只會奪人所愛的你們不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要保護自己的重要之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:13.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若我的聲音會使人痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:14.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:27.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能聽到我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不代表我也能聽到你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲音通過空氣振動傳播
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,影響對方的腦髓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想聽那種危險的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不擔心這傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:59.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想回消失的村莊時我就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:02.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想守護的幸福歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:05.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是囚禁她的牢籠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:09.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若能忘記這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受我方的條件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶走那個女人也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人是重要的愚者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:21.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要現在殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.09,0:11:24.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就萬事大吉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想上她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:38.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的聲音可是劇毒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在床上的嬌吟也聽不成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就連愛的嚶嚶細語
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:47.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都意味著你的死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:50.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛的嚶嚶細語
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:55.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯肯定希望我能贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放任那群笨蛋逍遙的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:01.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不可能會愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:12.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這座研究設施裡有很多機關
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:15.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牆上會「嗶嗶嗶」地射出激光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:18.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地板上會「唰」地射出長矛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天花板會「咚」地塌下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:21.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:22.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:34.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個房間是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:39.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:41.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我來守護
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:07.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可憐你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:15.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有任何寶貴之物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:17.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能獨自走向死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:19.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:22.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地板下射長矛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懸吊天花板？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:04.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你漫畫看多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:07.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都笑出眼淚來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:10.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙耳朵流血了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是你害的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:27.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:32.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:35.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:39.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是把你打入不幸深淵的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:50.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愛我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:02.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就親口告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:07.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:10.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:18.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:21.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:25.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:30.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:31.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:37.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:46.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:08.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個裝模作樣的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明知我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:25.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還敢說什麼贖罪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:38.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哈柯小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:40.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:50.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫外線100%阻隔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.17,0:16:52.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭的聲音也能完全遮斷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:57.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultra violet & noise cancelling helmet！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:04.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愚者還想談情說愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:09.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還早一萬兩千年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是一件道具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用來制裁迦南的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:35.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主動式噪音控制裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:40.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用波形相反的聲音抵消原聲的設備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.98,0:17:42.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要啟動這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除一人以外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人都不會受到哈柯的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:52.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人就是把一種感覺轉換成另一種的迦南
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:54.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.33,0:17:59.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在無聲的世界中心呼喚愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:01.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您指引我
