Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:36.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.03,0:18:39.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:42.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:45.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒有聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:49.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:53.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南的聯覺把聲音轉換成氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把顏色轉換成聽覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:57.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五感相互關聯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:18:59.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:02.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也能敏銳感知到哈柯的悲歎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:05.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將其再轉換成聲音傷害自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:41.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須和過去做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:45.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有個萬一…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:47.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:51.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請帶哈柯走出這場噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:45.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:47.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴上這個感覺好安心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:50.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:51.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:52.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有誇你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真是花園嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:58.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既陰暗又潮濕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不像開花的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:01.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然叫「{\1c&H00FF00}花園{\r}」但哪裡都沒有花…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:21.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺到了個不得了的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:26.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和冰箱一個味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:28.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:29.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰面碎了很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:34.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:54.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道不穿高跟鞋來了
